<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>Need one DBA (possibly 2) with technical and functional experience to analyze and assist client with upgrading the current Oracle eBusiness Suite R11.5.10.2 to R12.1+ and provide assistance as directed by the DBA team lead. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=2 face="Franklin Gothic Medium">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>Job Skills / Skill preferences are as follows: <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=2 face="Franklin Gothic Medium">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>1. Technical knowledge of Oracle eBusiness Suite Release 12.1+ specifically in the following modules: â€¢ Time and Labor â€¢ Core Human Resources (including payroll) â€¢ Advanced Benefits â€¢ Learning Management â€¢ Self-Service HR â€¢ iRecruitment <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>2. Experience with Oracle eBusiness Suite upgrade of the Oracle eBusiness Suite R12.1 <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>3. Experience with Oracle Database 9i through 11gR1. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>4. Experience with project planning and preparation for major release upgrades<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=2 face="Franklin Gothic Medium">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>Job Duties: <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></B></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><o:p><FONT size=2 face="Franklin Gothic Medium">&nbsp;</FONT></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>1. Research and apply patches for Oracle eBusiness upgrade. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>2. Assist with database management duties for 9i â€“ 11g databases. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>3. Perform compare/contrast analysis <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>4. Provide recommendation for strategic roadmap for upgrading <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>5. Assist in development of a project plan <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>6. Knowledge transfer to existing support team <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
