<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>15. Perform upgrade of Oracle Applications database from 9i to 11g. <o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial"><FONT face="Franklin Gothic Medium"><FONT size=2>16. Perform upgrade or Oracle Applications suite from 11.5.10.2. to 12.1+.<o:p></o:p></FONT></FONT></SPAN></P>
